<h3 id="id-(3.15)CustomerChannelAPI-​SendandReceivemessages"><span id="CustomerChannelAPI-SendandReceivemessages"></span><span id="id-(3.15)CustomerChannelAPI-send-n-receive"></span>​Send and Receive messages
